metadata.name: I-SOAR #1
metadata.description:
"I-SOAR" - Edition: 1 of 50 depicts the true nature of the real world. It establishes not only that we are all deeply interconnected—we are also deeply interdependent. I-SOAR declares that we are:

 One People – Traveling on One Planet – Toward One Common Future

-I-SOAR stands for the Interrelated Structure of All Reality, a quote from Dr. Martin Luther King JR 1967
